text: Louisa Adelaide Nott-Bower was an archer from Great Britain. She was born on 27 March 1861 and died on 6 September 1925. Nott-Bower competed at the 1908 Summer Olympics.Louisa Nott Bower == References == Category:1861 births Category:1925 deaths Category:Welsh sportspeople Category:British archers Category:Olympians for Great Britain
